'''Taris Control''' was the agency of the [[Taris Civil Authority]] that controlled all space traffic around [[Taris/Legends|Taris]].<ref name="KotOR4">[[Knights of the Old Republic 4|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 4]]</ref>

In [[3964 BBY]], Taris Control coordinated the pursuit of the starship [[The Last Resort (starship)|''The Last Resort'']] — transporting the fugitives [[Zayne Carrick]] and [[Marn Hierogryph]] — by [[Taris Civil Authority police cruiser]]s.<ref name="KotOR4" />

